These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, turquise, aquamarine, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, manager, software-developer, paramedic
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the fisherman is not to the left of the fisherman##8
 3. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the fisherman is not to the right of the fisherman##8
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person who likes black is between the manager and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the paramedic is the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the left of the paramedic##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the software-developer##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Color   | turquise | black   | grey   | aquamarine  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Job     | fisherman    | software-developer | manager     | paramedic    |

