.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, yellow, mauve, brown
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, ranch-style, colonial
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the ranch-style house is between the owner of the dog and the gothic-revival house##2
 2. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person who likes red is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the cape-cod house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
12. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
13. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
15. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person who likes red is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Color      | red | mauve | brown  | yellow  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| House   | gothic-revival    | ranch-style  | colonial | cape-cod |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

