.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: german, mexican, japanese, french
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, oliveros, blend, pall-mall
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the german##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the japanese##8
 7. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the japanese is on the left of the french##1
 9. the french is on the left of the mexican##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the german is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
12. the french is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Nationality   | german     | japanese  | french   | mexican      |
| Cigar   | oliveros | tiparillo    | blend      | pall-mall       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

