4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, chess, bridge
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the aristoff-smoker##6
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 3. the person eating plum is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the aristoff-smoker and the bongani-smoker##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 6. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
10. the bongani-smoker is the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
