The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 2. the russian is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person driving the airplane##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 8. the malaysian is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
10. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person driving the bike and the person drinking almond-milk##2
12. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
