10. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
