.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
4 different pets are kept: rat, horse, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, puzzles, traveling
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
11. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Pet   | rat  | lizard      | hedgehog     | horse     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Hobby     | collecting     | puzzles | traveling | hiking     |

