.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, sprite
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, goldfish, horse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, indie, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
10. the fan of indie is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of trance is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
14. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola      | sprite  | soy-milk | juice        |
| Pet         | horse | rabbit   | lizard   | goldfish |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | house   | indie    | dubstep      |
| Sport   | skateboarding   | swimming | surfing   | parkour    |

