.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, purple, brown, light-blue
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, musician, police-officer
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, dancing, video-games, card-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who likes white##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 6. the person driving the van is the person who likes purple##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color    | purple          | white | brown        | light-blue    |
| Job         | police-officer | doctor   | electrician | musician  |
| Hobby         | video-games           | collecting     | card-games       | dancing  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

