.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, badminton, weightlifting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, horror, lacrossesy
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, photographer, project-manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, subway
 1. the person watching horror movies is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
 2. the dancer is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person watching lacrossesy movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the dancer is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching lacrossesy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the project-manager##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Sport    | badminton        | lacrosse        | skateboarding        | weightlifting   |
| Movie-Genre       | romance      | scientific      | lacrossesy | horror |
| Job         | project-manager | photographer | fisherman     | dancer  |
| Transport   | roller          | jet-ski      | quad-bike     | subway  |

