.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, boat, scooter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, rose, dahlia, iris
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person driving the boat##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 8. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person driving the boat and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Transport           | quad-bike | train    | boat | scooter    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Flower   | aconite   | dahlia      | rose         | iris     |

 